java.lang.Object
org.cyclops.everlastingabilities.api.capability.ItemStackMutableAbilityStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAbilityStore, IMutableAbilityStore, IMutableAbilityStoreRegistryAccess
public class ItemStackMutableAbilityStore extends Object implements IMutableAbilityStoreRegistryAccess
Wrapper for an item ability store. TODO: This is just to avoid a Forge bug where cap NBT is not always sent to the client.
